# College Attendance Tracker

A comprehensive attendance tracking application built with React, Express, and PostgreSQL. Helps students track class attendance, set goals, and manage academic schedules with Chrome notifications.

## ‚ú® Features

- **Simple Authentication**: Name-based login (no passwords)
- **Smart Calculations**: Class-based attendance tracking (not day-based)
- **Goal Setting**: Set attendance percentage targets with feasibility analysis
- **Chrome Notifications**: Daily reminders and progress alerts
- **Calendar View**: Interactive calendar with color-coded attendance
- **Schedule Management**: Weekly class schedules with time slots
- **Holiday Management**: Mark holidays to exclude from calculations
- **Mobile Responsive**: Works perfectly on all devices
- **Data Persistence**: PostgreSQL database with real-time sync

